{{dcl begin}}
{{dcl | num=1 | since=c++23 |
const_reverse_iterator rend()  const noexcept;
}}
{{dcl | num=2 | since=c++23 |
const_reverse_iterator crend() const noexcept;
}}
{{dcl end}}

Returns a reverse iterator pointing past the last entry of the reversed {{tt|basic_stacktrace}}. It corresponds to the iterator preceding the first entry of the original {{tt|basic_stacktrace}}. This iterator acts as a placeholder, attempting to dereference it results in undefined behavior.

{{image|range-rbegin-rend.svg}}

===Parameters===
(none)

===Return value===
The end iterator of the reversed {{tt|basic_stacktrace}}.

===Complexity===
Constant.
